    <h1>The Bitcoin Trilemma</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Why Bitcoin deliberately sacrifices speed — and why that's exactly right</p>
    <p class="intro-text">Every blockchain must choose: you can optimize for any two of three foundational properties — <strong>Decentralization</strong>, <strong>Security</strong>, and <strong>Scalability</strong> — but never all three at the base layer. Click each vertex below to explore the tradeoffs.</p>
